page.title: 21Update of Graham Prigg
page.content: Now 30 years old i am currently a Professional Magician living in Cullompton, not far from Clyst Hydon. I travel all over the country performing at weddings,parties and other special events. I left Clyst Hydon scool in 1991 to go to Secondry education at Cullompton Community college. I lived in The village of Clyst hydon from 1980- 1990.
